The paper deals with interactive learning from human feedback, which is a problem that falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The learning is done on a physical robot, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the influence of human trainers on the learner's policy, which is a topic related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Finally, the paper uses image features to learn behaviors, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV).
